::Striker::

Striker blinks as Spears slams the door in his face. She was obvioustly not 
'fine'. She looked and sounded far from it. He sighs. He should let her calm 
down. Or... An idea occurs to him. Perhaps she can take her anger out on 
him....

He knocks on the door again. "Hey, you still up for that holo-room training?"
